      <title>美国银行业巨头摩根大通选举好时首席执行官米歇尔·巴克加入董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banking-giant-jpmorgan-elects-hershey-ceo-michele-buck-board-2024-12-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行巨头摩根大通周四宣布，选举好时公司首席执行官米歇尔巴克 (Michele Buck) 加入其董事会，该任命将于 3 月 17 日起生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-banking-giant-jpmorgan-elects-hershey-ceo-michele-buck-board-2024-12-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 21:59:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
